(Changing Room, Men's)

567
00:31:58,090 --> 00:31:59,240
You're trying to make me talk.

568
00:31:59,730 --> 00:32:02,570
My strongest attribute is that
I don't gossip.

569
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:04,570
I have no comment.

