00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:15,660
(Beiya Hospital)

571
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:27,280
Good morning, Mr. Ning.

572
00:32:27,930 --> 00:32:29,000
Wait!

573
00:32:30,690 --> 00:32:32,160
Wait up!

574
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,240
Thanks.

575
00:32:33,450 --> 00:32:34,690
Morning.

576
00:32:34,690 --> 00:32:35,180
- Good morning.
- Morning.

577
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,090
Morning, guys.

578
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:38,850
Mr. Ning,

579
00:32:38,970 --> 00:32:40,520
Dr. Qian scheduled a surgery

580
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:41,810
where I'll be the head surgeon.

581
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,240
I'm pretty nervous.

582
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:45,280
Were you nervous when you led surgery
for the first time?

583
00:32:45,490 --> 00:32:46,330
Yes, I was.

584
00:32:46,690 --> 00:32:48,000
Dr. Ding is going
to perform her first surgery.

585
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,460
This outstanding graduate
of John Hopkins

586
00:32:49,460 --> 00:32:50,400
sure is impressive.

587
00:32:51,570 --> 00:32:52,280
Ruan,

588
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:53,400
the university's anniversary
is in a few days.

589
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,120
Are you going?

590
00:32:54,210 --> 00:32:55,690
I'll go if nothing comes up.

591
00:32:57,090 --> 00:32:58,730
They say medical students have it rough.

592
00:32:58,730 --> 00:33:00,330
Baldness comes
before fulfilling our goals.

593
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:01,930
You don't seem
to have a hair loss problem.

594
00:33:01,930 --> 00:33:03,240
It seems your hair is thicker
than before.

595
00:33:03,930 --> 00:33:04,810
Also, you're still the same

596
00:33:04,810 --> 00:33:05,930
after so many years.

597
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:07,490
You've become younger.

598
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,850
Everyone looks young
during their studies

599
00:33:09,850 --> 00:33:11,090
and grows older when they graduate.

600
00:33:11,090 --> 00:33:11,810
But look at you.

601
00:33:11,810 --> 00:33:13,040
You practically become younger.

602
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:13,850
You don't look too bad yourself.

603
00:33:13,850 --> 00:33:15,520
You're more handsome than before.

604
00:33:15,850 --> 00:33:16,450
Really?

605
00:33:16,810 --> 00:33:18,160
Ning, have I become more handsome?

606
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,610
Yes, you've always looked this handsome.

607
00:33:20,450 --> 00:33:21,040
Dr. Ruan,

608
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,360
please come early for the rounds.

609
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:22,970
Okay.

610
00:33:33,570 --> 00:33:34,360
Dr. Ning.

611
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,690
The patient underwent a reduction
depressed skull fracture treatment.

612
00:33:37,690 --> 00:33:38,300
We've re-examined the skull

613
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:39,000
with a CT scan once.

614
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:40,400
We've submitted his blood,
liver and kidney functions,

615
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:41,810
and blood electrolytes for examination.

616
00:33:42,570 --> 00:33:44,330
The dressing should be changed
every two to three days.

617
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:46,120
Today is the day to change it, right?

618
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:46,640
Yes.

619
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:47,810
Dr. Ning,
I'll make the arrangement later.

620
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:54,040
Bed 13 underwent drilling
and drainage for craniocerebral trauma.

621
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,040
It's been ten days since the surgery.

622
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:55,860
Based on the CT scan,

623
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:56,760
the blood clot is gone.

624
00:33:57,810 --> 00:33:58,640
Hey, kid.

625
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,330
You're still recovering.

626
00:34:00,330 --> 00:34:01,210
You should eat plain food

627
00:34:01,210 --> 00:34:03,000
instead of cakes like this. Understand?

628
00:34:03,090 --> 00:34:05,450
But today is my birthday.

629
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:08,360
Can't I eat a little?

630
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:09,880
Not even on your birthday.

631
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:10,770
Don't forget, okay?

632
00:34:11,770 --> 00:34:12,640
Fei,

633
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:13,690
time for an IV.

634
00:34:13,690 --> 00:34:14,730
No, I don't want to do it.

635
00:34:14,730 --> 00:34:15,880
I don't want to do the IV.

636
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:16,600
You must do it.

637
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:17,730
Or else you'll get infected.

638
00:34:17,930 --> 00:34:18,530
The doctor is right.

639
00:34:18,730 --> 00:34:19,560
Be good.

640
00:34:19,930 --> 00:34:21,160
Cai Jinrong, age 65.

641
00:34:21,160 --> 00:34:22,400
She suffers from blurred vision.

642
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,320
The vision range of the right eye

643
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,770
is less than one meter.

644
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:26,530
The vision on the left is only 0.5.

645
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:28,290
The lesion is located
in the front of the suprasellar cistern,

646
00:34:28,290 --> 00:34:30,120
which is closely related
to the optic nerve on both sides.

647
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,120
Madam,

648
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:33,010
try and look at my eyes.

649
00:34:33,010 --> 00:34:34,970
Can you see these two fingers?

650
00:34:36,250 --> 00:34:37,160
You can't see them at all?

651
00:34:37,290 --> 00:34:38,640
Can you see if they're here?

652
00:34:41,010 --> 00:34:41,970
You can't see the one on the left?

653
00:34:45,770 --> 00:34:47,160
We must remove pituitary tumors

654
00:34:47,450 --> 00:34:48,250
as soon as possible.

655
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,160
Doctor,

656
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:52,490
must I do the surgery?

657
00:34:52,930 --> 00:34:54,210
Can I not do it?

658
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:55,840
You must do this surgery.

659
00:34:56,050 --> 00:34:57,010
If this continues,

660
00:34:57,010 --> 00:34:58,210
your eyesight will worsen,

661
00:34:58,210 --> 00:34:59,450
and you may go blind, understand?

662
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:00,730
Did her family sign the consent form?

663
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,050
We were not able
to get in touch with them.

664
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,840
The neighborhood committee
sent her here.

665
00:35:04,250 --> 00:35:05,730
We tried contacting her son.

666
00:35:06,210 --> 00:35:07,400
When he knew it was from the hospital,

667
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,080
he hung up immediately.

668
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:10,320
Find a way to contact the family.

669
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,250
We must do this surgery
as soon as possible.

670
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,800
Mr. Ning,

671
00:35:22,210 --> 00:35:23,840
shouldn't you help

672
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:25,080
when we weren't able to
reach Madam Cai's family?

673
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:26,530
Her children are outrageous.

674
00:35:26,530 --> 00:35:27,880
Are you a doctor or a judge?

675
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:29,320
Do you have too much free time
lately?

676
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,120
How did it go?

677
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:40,290
It must be exhausting doing rounds
with Ning Zhiqian.

678
00:35:40,560 --> 00:35:41,730
Can you manage?

679
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:45,050
I'm two years behind others,

680
00:35:45,490 --> 00:35:47,930
and at least four years
behind Ding Yiyuan.

681
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:50,010
She's already performing surgeries.
So I need to work harder.

682
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,600
Well.

683
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:52,970
If you didn't divorce back then,

684
00:35:52,970 --> 00:35:54,010
your kid would have grown up.

685
00:35:54,450 --> 00:35:55,690
Well, he has a son.

686
00:35:55,930 --> 00:35:56,880
How is that the same?

687
00:35:58,010 --> 00:35:59,120
Speaking of that,

688
00:35:59,120 --> 00:36:00,690
it's not easy for Ning Zhiqian too.

689
00:36:01,530 --> 00:36:03,400
All these years,
he took care of everything

690
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,690
to raise the kid,

691
00:36:04,690 --> 00:36:05,930
even closer than birth parents.

692
00:36:08,690 --> 00:36:09,840
Ning Xiang isn't his biological son?

693
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,600
You didn't know?

694
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:14,160
Didn't he tell you?

695
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,800
Ning Zhiqian adopted Ning Xiang.

696
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:20,250
When the kid was three months old,

697
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:22,010
someone abandoned him
in the hospital's corridor.

698
00:36:22,640 --> 00:36:23,770
We even found he had a brain tumor.

699
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:27,080
Ning Zhiqian did the surgery.

700
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,690
The child was so young

701
00:36:28,690 --> 00:36:30,800
and needed special care
after the surgery.

702
00:36:31,010 --> 00:36:32,560
He didn't trust anyone
to take care of the kid.

703
00:36:32,930 --> 00:36:34,080
So he did it himself.

704
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:37,010
He was both the mom and the dad.

705
00:36:38,970 --> 00:36:40,450
Didn't he try to find the mom?

706
00:36:40,730 --> 00:36:42,050
He did.

707
00:36:42,050 --> 00:36:43,640
But there was no clue at all.

708
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:53,320
This being said,

709
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:54,400
Ning Zhiqian

710
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:56,320
should find a mom for Ning Xiang now.

711
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,210
Liuzheng,

712
00:36:58,400 --> 00:36:59,730
why don't you think about it?

713
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:02,210
After all, you had feelings
for each other back then.

714
00:37:04,730 --> 00:37:05,360
No.

715
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:12,880
I just want to tell you this today.

716
00:37:13,120 --> 00:37:15,360
You weren't here before.

717
00:37:15,450 --> 00:37:16,690
Huang Qian from
the Internal Medicine Department

718
00:37:17,050 --> 00:37:18,050
asked me to find out

719
00:37:18,050 --> 00:37:19,360
about Ning Zhiqian's marital status.

720
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,490
After she found out he was single,

721
00:37:21,730 --> 00:37:23,080
she asked me to bring them two together.

722
00:37:23,490 --> 00:37:25,080
So I brought it up to Ning Zhiqian,

723
00:37:25,080 --> 00:37:26,290
and he declined me right away.

724
00:37:26,690 --> 00:37:28,050
But this morning,

725
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:31,010
Ning Zhiqian asked me
to introduce someone to him.

726
00:37:35,210 --> 00:37:36,250
Isn't that great?

727
00:37:39,450 --> 00:37:42,160
That's why I'm discussing this with you.

728
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:43,560
If you don't want him
to find someone new,

729
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:44,970
I can ruin his chance for you.

730
00:37:44,970 --> 00:37:46,320
You better don't mess around.

731
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:48,970
It's none of my business.

732
00:37:48,970 --> 00:37:50,250
Don't ruin it for him.

733
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:55,530
Are you sure you don't mind?

734
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,010
Why would I mind?

735
00:37:58,640 --> 00:38:00,290
Why don't you introduce one to me?

736
00:38:00,290 --> 00:38:01,400
Sure.

737
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,800
What kind of guy do you like?

738
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,290
Tall and rich?

739
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:06,360
A modest and self-disciplined man?

740
00:38:07,490 --> 00:38:08,840
Tall and slender?

741
00:38:10,050 --> 00:38:11,360
Don't all these describe Ning Zhiqian?

742
00:38:12,930 --> 00:38:13,970
Just eat your lunch.

743
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:37,260
(Old Street Li)

744
00:38:38,210 --> 00:38:39,160
Hello there, Dr. Ding.

745
00:38:39,450 --> 00:38:40,800
Did you just finish your night shift?

746
00:38:42,250 --> 00:38:43,880
Did you just finish
your night shift too?

747
00:38:46,770 --> 00:38:48,490
Your appearance is shocking.

748
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:52,290
A middle-aged man like you
shouldn't eat deep-fried dough sticks.

749
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,560
It's good.

750
00:38:56,730 --> 00:38:58,120
Say, Vice President Ding sure

751
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,930
is devoted to his career.

752
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,840
He even named his kid Hospital Ding.
[*Yiyuan: rhymes with hospital]

753
00:39:03,530 --> 00:39:04,320
Sorry about that.

754
00:39:04,560 --> 00:39:05,400
I mean, Ding Yiyuan.

755
00:39:06,450 --> 00:39:07,970
Your name may be Hospital Ding.

756
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:09,210
Sorry. I mean, Ding Yiyuan.

757
00:39:10,010 --> 00:39:12,450
But the Ding Family
doesn't own the hospital.

758
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:15,080
The doctors at the hospital
aren't all from the Ding Family too.

759
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:15,880
So

760
00:39:16,290 --> 00:39:18,400
your dad may keep you away
from suffering.

761
00:39:18,930 --> 00:39:20,640
But he can't save you from vinegar.
[*Vinegar: rhymes with jealous]

762
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:22,250
No, thank you.

763
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,400
I may enjoy vinegar.

764
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,080
But I don't just get jealous of anyone.

765
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:28,080
I've been meaning to ask.

766
00:39:28,290 --> 00:39:29,880
What do you see in Ning?

767
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,640
I thought your strongest attribute

768
00:39:32,010 --> 00:39:33,250
is not gossiping.

769
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:36,250
You're left
with no positive attribute now.

770
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,010
Okay.

771
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:39,800
Eat up.

772
00:39:40,250 --> 00:39:41,210
I'm done.

773
00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:42,210
Enjoy your meal.

774
00:39:45,490 --> 00:39:46,080
See you.

775
00:39:50,250 --> 00:39:51,640
Such a spoiled heiress.

776
00:39:51,640 --> 00:39:52,970
What a waste.

777
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:56,560
Let's go.

778
00:39:56,930 --> 00:39:58,840
Wang Qiantong!

779
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:01,640
- Don't run.
- This will be the last time.

780
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:02,400
No more next time.

781
00:40:02,970 --> 00:40:04,120
You better explain it to him.

782
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:07,210
Actually, you didn't

783
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,880
have to come today.

784
00:40:09,970 --> 00:40:11,360
What? Why are you so fickle-minded?

785
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,730
You begged me to come first.

786
00:40:13,450 --> 00:40:15,210
Begging you to come is my problem.

787
00:40:15,210 --> 00:40:16,640
It's up to you to come here.

788
00:40:18,050 --> 00:40:19,880
I didn't want Ning Xiang
to feel embarrassed.

789
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:21,080
Also, you better explain it

790
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:22,560
to him earlier.

791
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,400
He has the right to know
who his birth mother is.

792
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:26,080
Mom!

793
00:40:26,080 --> 00:40:28,800
This is my best friend, Wang Qiantong.

794
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,530
Wang Qiantong,

795
00:40:29,530 --> 00:40:30,730
this is my mom.

796
00:40:30,730 --> 00:40:31,600
Hello, madam.

797
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:33,450
- Hello.
- So you're Ning Xiang's mom.

798
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:36,210
Qiantong is a good friend of
Ning Xiang's.

799
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:39,080
I think it's the first time
we're meeting you.

800
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:40,080
Yes.

801
00:40:40,080 --> 00:40:41,530
Ning Xiang looks like you.

802
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,730
Hello, Ms. Zhou.

803
00:40:47,730 --> 00:40:48,400
Hello, Ning Xiang.

804
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,770
This is my mom.

805
00:40:49,770 --> 00:40:50,490
Hello, Miss.

806
00:40:50,490 --> 00:40:52,970
She's here to accompany me
to the sports meet.

807
00:40:52,970 --> 00:40:54,840
Both my dad and mom are here.

808
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:55,560
That's great.

809
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:57,360
Then make sure
to do your best in the race later.

810
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,290
I now announce

811
00:41:01,730 --> 00:41:04,450
the Parent-Child Sports Meet
of Cosmo Bilingual Kindergarten

812
00:41:04,450 --> 00:41:06,360
begins!

813
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,690
- Yay!
- Yay!

814
00:41:09,050 --> 00:41:09,880
The first event

815
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,970
is Sedan Chair Race!

816
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:14,010
Parents, please get ready.

817
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,080
Be careful.

818
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:15,970
Okay.

819
00:41:16,290 --> 00:41:17,210
All right, everyone.

820
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,360
On your marks!

821
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,210
We're going to run soon.

822
00:41:19,490 --> 00:41:20,400
Get set!

823
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:22,530
Go!

824
00:41:22,530 --> 00:41:23,800
- Go!
- Go!

825
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:25,460
Run faster!

826
00:41:25,460 --> 00:41:27,700
Dad! Mom! Faster!

827
00:41:27,940 --> 00:41:29,700
Dad, run!

828
00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:30,820
Turn!

829
00:41:33,580 --> 00:41:35,780
Come on. Run faster!

830
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,340
I'm okay.

831
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:42,600
It's your fault.

832
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:43,800
It's okay.
We'll do better in the next race.

833
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:44,530
We'll put in more effort.

834
00:41:44,530 --> 00:41:45,080
It's all right.

835
00:41:45,080 --> 00:41:45,560
Let's do this.

836
00:41:46,210 --> 00:41:47,320
We'll do better in the next race.

